data.description: Tucked into a quiet tree lined cul-de-sac resides this beautifully updated home on a generously sized .287-acre lot. A gated private courtyard & patio greet you upon entering. Inside the foyers connects you to the formal dining & spacious living room partitioned by the double fireplace. Adjacent to living room is the breakfast nook & kitchen with granite countertops, freshly painted cabinets, brass hardware and new recessed lighting. Office area and full-sized utility room separate kitchen from attached 2car garage. Primary bedroom is accented with a vaulted ceiling, door leading to private backyard patio & updated bathroom w walk-in frameless glass shower. Backyard lends the ideal space to unwind or entertain w plenty of grass space, landscaping & patio area. Updates you’ll love include the plantation shutters, decorative chandeliers, new AC units & new SS appliances. Community pool, tennis courts & playground. Quick access to restaurants & grocers on Westheimer + city center shopping
